  <title>WebKit2.Settings.allow_file_access_from_file_urls</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
Settings.allow_file_access_from_file_urls: Boolean (Read / Write / Construct)
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Whether file access is allowed from file URLs. By default, when
something is loaded in a <link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/> using a file URI, cross
origin requests to other file resources are not allowed. This
setting allows you to change that behaviour, so that it would be
possible to do a XMLHttpRequest of a local file, for example.</p>
  <p>Since 2.10</p>
